|------|--------|
| `schema/migrations/20260304_task_source_session.surql` | **New file.** Migration to add `source_session` field and ASSERT on task status. |
| `schema/surreal-schema.surql` | Add `DEFINE FIELD source_session ON task TYPE option<record<agent_session>>;` and ASSERT constraint on status. |
| `app/src/server/mcp/mcp-queries.ts` | Set `source_session` in `createAgentSession()`, clear it in `endAgentSession()`. |
